  <titles>
    <title type="short" as="introduced">Performing Arts Labor Relations Amendments</title>
    <title type="official" as="introduced">A bill to amend the National Labor Relations Act to give employers and performers in the performing arts rights given by section 8(e) of such Act to employers and employees in similarly situated industries, to give to employers and performers in the performing arts the same rights given by section 8(f) of such Act to employers and employees in the construction industry, and for other purposes.</title>
